data.description: This is a renovated modern single-family home in a quiet neighborhood in Palmland Homestead with a spacious 5-bedrooms and 3-bathrooms. Recent renovations include porcelain floors, kitchen, bathrooms, fence, and an open terrace with a BBQ and outdoor kitchen. This home has a new roof from 2022 and plenty of space to park a boat/RV. This home comes completely furnished and is ready to move-in.
